'''Bamford–Stevens反应'''（班福德-史蒂芬斯反应）

[[醛|醛]]或[[酮|酮]]的[[对甲苯磺酰|对甲苯磺酰]][[腙|腙]]用[[强碱|强碱]]处理时，发生[[消除|消除]]生成[[烯烃|烯烃]]。<ref name="bamford1952">{{cite journal en| author = Bamford, W. R.; Stevens, T. S. | journal = [[Journal_of_the_Chemical_Society|J. Chem. Soc.]] | date = 1952 | pages = 4735–4740 | title = The decomposition of toluene-p-sulfonylhydrazones by alkali | doi = 10.1039/JR9520004735}}</ref><ref name="shapiro1976">{{cite book en| last = Shapiro | first = R. H.| title = Organic Reactions | date = March 1976 | volume = 23 | pages = 405–507 | chapter = Alkenes from Tosylhydrazones  | publisher = Wiley | location = New York }} ISBN 0-471-19624-X.</ref><ref name="adlington1983">{{cite journal en| author = Adlington, R. M.; Barrett, A. G. M. | journal = [[Accounts_of_Chemical_Research|Acc. Chem. Res.]] | year = 1983 | volume = 16 | issue = 2 | pages = 55–59 | title = Recent applications of the Shapiro reaction | doi = 10.1021/ar00086a004}}</ref> 

<br />
